Unfortunatly I am in the middle of a month long move.
I will definatly be back in early June, but I do not
know when. So for everybody that is interacting with
my characters, I'm sorry. Here's how I'm going to
split it up:

Magmatron-nobody, he's going to sit in his room and
pout

Spy Streak-Rudra
Cerberus, Nightblade: They got stuck in transit to the
Destron Base Sulaco, they'll get there soon.

Dachande-Alloran because he controls Battera.


In charge of the Destrons will be Cygnar and
Apocalypse, work togther, do not bicker with one
another. Try to get the Deathsaurus back to
operational performance. Then Cygnar will be in charge
of that area and Apocalypse will be in charge of the
Sulaco. Do not do anything without consulting the
other. Thank you.

Somebody should go get Hulicgen and the new Destron. 

Overall have fun, this is the only time I could get on
the computer at school and I already have like 600 e-mails.
